OL,3,CDrunk driver avoids prison after
OL,4,Ccrashing into car and fleeing the scene
OL,6,FA man in Jersey has been sentenced to
OL,7,F312 hours of community service for
OL,8,Fcausing serious injury whilst drink
OL,9,Fdriving.
OL,11,FJersey's Royal Court heard how Pedro
OL,12,FNuno Rodrigues Caires was on his way
OL,13,Fhome from a christening where he had
OL,14,Fbeen drinking, when he crashed into a
OL,15,Fstationary Toyota Yaris, seriously
OL,16,Finjuring the driver.
OL,18,FCCTV footage captured the 39 year-old
OL,19,Freaching speeds of 80mph on Queens
OL,20,FRoad shortly before the incident on
OL,21,Fthe evening of Sunday 9 of July.
