OL,3,CDrunk driver avoids prison after
OL,4,Ccrashing into car and fleeing the scene
OL,6,FExtensive damage was caused to both
OL,7,Fvehicles and the walls of the
OL,8,Fsurrounding properties due to the
OL,9,Fimpact.
OL,11,FCaires fled the scene on foot, running
OL,12,Fhome.
OL,14,FThe driver of the Yaris was a takeaway
OL,15,Fdelivery driver who was found
OL,16,Funconscious at the scene - he regained
OL,17,Fconsciousness before being taken to
OL,18,Fhospital.
