OL,3,CDrunk driver avoids prison after
OL,4,Ccrashing into car and fleeing the scene
OL,6,FCaires was arrested at his home
OL,7,Faddress in the early hours of the
OL,8,Ffollowing morning, where he was found
OL,9,Fto be over the legal drink drive limit.
OL,11,FThe court heard how the victim
OL,12,Fsuffered bruises on the brain and
OL,13,Fother minor physical injuries but was
OL,14,Freleased from hospital 48 hours after
OL,15,Fthe incident.
OL,17,FHowever, he continued to suffer with
OL,18,Fdizziness and had periods of insomnia.
