OL,3,CDrunk driver avoids prison after
OL,4,Ccrashing into car and fleeing the scene
OL,6,FOnly one of the drivers injuries fell
OL,7,Fwithin the 'serious injury' category,
OL,8,Fbeing bruises to the brain.
OL,10,FThe defendant was inconsolable in the
OL,11,Fdock, sobbing audibly throughout the
OL,12,Fhearing.
OL,14,FCaires pleaded guilty to driving a
OL,15,Fmotor vehicle with alcohol
OL,16,Fconcentration above the prescribed
OL,17,Flimit, causing serious injury by
OL,18,Fdangerous driving, and failing to stop
OL,19,Fand report an accident.
