OL,3,CDrunk driver avoids prison after
OL,4,Ccrashing into car and fleeing the scene
OL,6,FThe prosecution suggested a sentence
OL,7,Fof 3 years in prison but due to the
OL,8,Fdelay in court proceedings the Bailiff
OL,9,Fsaid the defendant had already
OL,10,F"suffered an extra punishment" and had
OL,11,Fshown "clear and genuine remorse",
OL,12,Fmitigating his sentence.
OL,14,FHe has been sentenced to 312 hours of
OL,15,Fcommunity service and been
OL,16,Fdisqualified from driving for 2 years
OL,17,Fand 6 months.
